vice on first car, Went to buy a new car a few years later, fellow said he would ring back. Never did. Got a mazda instead.", "time" : 1706745524, "translated" : false }, { "author_name" : "Polar Express", "author_url" : "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105348442368259693434/reviews", "language" : "en", "original_language" : "en", "profile_photo_url" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-hl8M9HNz9M9fSpwJ2cVApYB3M46Hwz9SXLGlP2-NSsAdtLo=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating" : 5, "relative_time_description" : "4 years ago", "text" : "Fantastic service by Stuart at Hyundai in Sale. He was very knowledgeable and more than happy to go above and beyond to do his best on price and get the right car that suits. Being honest about the cars and there features made it easy to buy one through him.", "time" : 1640201542, "translated" : false }, { "author_name" : "ALLAN RANKIN", "author_url" : "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114619801661259779189/reviews", "language" : "en", "original_language" : "en", "profile_photo_url" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK8GaBLBpFQthJmUd8ePf33Lf-9Pyl37oVlgGZWBwAtyx4wODM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2", "rating" : 5, "relative_time_description" : "3 years ago", "text" : "The sales manager at Sale Hyundai was excellent to deal with. He kept us up to date with the pre delivery process and timing for us to pick the car up when it was ready to go.", "time" : 1665998472, "translated" : false }, { "author_name" : "Margaret Osborn", "author_url" : "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108317138511976722426/reviews", "language" : "en", "original_language" : "en", "profile_photo_url" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJgaJbwAQcbVEO6c1fAd8tRoFelm0gCgKWYrQfD7JCszrygig=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo", "rating" : 5, "relative_time_description" : "7 years ago", "text" : "Excellent service and helpfull very happy with what we purchased keep it up you guys and thankyou", "time" : 1526984728, "translated" : false } ], "types" : [ "car_dealer", "car_repair", "establishment", "point_of_interest", "store" ], "url" : "https://maps.google.com/?cid=11257746867135396581", "user_ratings_total" : 13, "utc_offset" : 660, "vicinity" : "36/38 Foster St, Sale", "website" : "http://salehyundai.com.au/", "wheelchair_accessible_entrance" : true }, "status" : "OK"}